n a blockchain ecosystem. This way, it greatly reduces the risk of system\noutages due to SPoFs, by allowing peer-to-peer conflict resolution, and being\nmore resilient to failures in the ground communication infrastructure.\nFurthermore, it provides priority-based balancing mechanisms that help to\nregulate fairness among participants in the utilization of the airspace.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Aug 2022 12:54:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-22"}
