 can precisely locate the\nscaleups that have a great potential return in 2 to 5 years. Furthermore, our\nqualitative inspection illustrates some advantageous attributes of the SiRE\nrevenue forecasts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Aug 2022 00:20:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 23 Aug 2022 12:38:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 26 Sep 2022 21:33:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-28"}
